  "url" 

} 

 

In our example, the metadata of ​Image A ​and ​Image B ​are both stored in IPFS as ​content                                   
metadata objects​, which further refers to the corresponding ​content creator objects                     
and ​service provider objects​. The IPFS addresses of the ​content metadata objects                       
are ​zdpuB1JCLTPNYA7TmedHVR4Py6s2HcXXXZvvg9tNWX3yKayMp and     
